oat.com/blog/2026/07/harvard-scientists-turned-a-silicon-chip-into-a-dna-factory</link><description>哈佛大学的科学家们制造了一种可以利用电和水写入 DNA 的硅芯片，为 DNA 制造和生物技术带来了更清洁的未来。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/harvard-scientists-turned-a-silicon-chip-into-a-dna-factory.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/harvard-scientists-turned-a-silicon-chip-into-a-dna-factory</guid></item><item><title>预测 2050 年：新兴技术的融合力量</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/predicting-2050-the-convergent-power-of-emerging-technologies</link><description>亲爱的朋友们和同事们， 在本期题为“预测 2050 年：新兴技术的融合力量”的安全与技术洞察时事通讯中，我提供了有关我们的世界在不远的将来在技术上可能呈现的样子的见解。我从之前的著作和播客中整理了大部分内容，它们是我的观点。我很高兴收到您的反馈，以及您认为将影响我们 2050 年生活的想法。谢谢查克·布鲁克斯 (Chuck Brooks)。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/predicting-2050-the-convergent-power-of-emerging-technologies.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/predicting-2050-the-convergent-power-of-emerging-technologies</guid></item><item><title>人工智能时代的网络卫生——我们的数字防御第一道防线</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/cyber-hygiene-in-the-ai-era-our-first-line-of-digital-defense</link><description>查克·布鲁克斯&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cyber-hygiene-in-the-ai-era-our-first-line-of-digital-defense.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/cyber-hygiene-in-the-ai-era-our-first-line-of-digital-defense</guid></item><item><title>航天器可以安全地绕黑洞运行多远？比较致命的恒星质量黑洞与温和的超大质量巨星</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-close-can-a-spacecraft-safely-orbit-a-black-hole-compare-deadly-stellar-mass-black-holes-with-gentler-supermassive-giants</link><description>看看极限轨道如何为未来的船舶带来巨大的速度提升。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/isaac-arthur-isaac_a_arthur-instagram-reel.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-close-can-a-spacecraft-safely-orbit-a-black-hole-compare-deadly-stellar-mass-black-holes-with-gentler-supermassive-giants</guid></item><item><title>瓶子里的微小宇宙揭示了生命起源的线索</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-tiny-universe-in-a-bottle-reveals-clues-to-the-origins-of-life</link><description>研究人员通过在玻璃管内重建类似太空的条件，从头开始创造了宇宙尘埃。这些尘埃含有由生命必需元素构成的复杂的富碳分子，并产生类似于太空中发现的真实物质的红外信号。通过研究这些实验室样本，科学家可以探索恒星周围的有机化学如何展开，以及彗星、小行星和陨石如何将这些成分带到地球。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-tiny-universe-in-a-bottle-reveals-clues-to-the-origins-of-life.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 23:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-tiny-universe-in-a-bottle-reveals-clues-to-the-origins-of-life</guid></item><item><title>随着年龄的增长，恢复清除僵尸细胞的能力可能会让我们保持敏锐</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/restoring-ability-to-remove-zombie-cells-may-keep-us-sharp-as-we-age</link><description>随着年龄的增长，僵尸细胞或衰老细胞会在我们体内积聚，而我们清除它们的能力就会减弱。但一项针对小鼠的研究表明，一种药物可以恢复这种能力并改善衰老结果&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/restoring-ability-to-remove-zombie-cells-may-keep-us-sharp-as-we-age.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 23:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/restoring-ability-to-remove-zombie-cells-may-keep-us-sharp-as-we-age</guid></item><item><title>尼尔·里默 (Neil Rimer) 认为人工智能资金正在回归</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/neil-rimer-thinks-the-ai-money-is-coming-back-out</link><description>Index Ventures 联合创始人、风险投资家尼尔·里默 (Neil Rimer) 预测，人工智能在硅谷创造的历史性财富将不得不重新分配，无论是自愿还是非自愿。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/neil-rimer-thinks-the-ai-money-is-coming-back-out.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 23:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/neil-rimer-thinks-the-ai-money-is-coming-back-out</guid></item></channel></rss>